          "datePublished": "2025-10-08",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Over last two years it has become the worst school - teachers are nice and cooperative but they can’t do much when the principal and admin staff is so rude. Principal doesn’t have a way to talk - neither with parents nor with children. School has become only a money minting machine and nothing else… they would make sure they increase fee everywhere by almost 10% but when parents Have issues and want to share feedback they are just not receptive. Principal has even made disrespectful remarks when tried to meet in person and share feedback. In another few years I see this school reducing to nothing. It will also destroy xaviers name. Half of the good reviews here have been made by school teachers itself and I am sure it is done intentionally to manipulate the reviews. The directors need to be concerned as it’s the reputation at stake now but guess they are happy as they are making truck loads of money at the cost of kids. Pathetic staff. ",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
