            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter has been studying since nursery it’s been 5 years with xaviers. Initially until 2024 the school was one of the best …. However post some management changes its becomes worse especially the Tera hers the staff including the principal and headmistress they are all so rude and unapproachable it has almost become a pain so much so that most parents want to quit and I personally advise others to not get their kids admitted in the school. ",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
